{"article_id":"h482kll6PsQTAmS2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"John O. Brennan , President Obama ' s pick","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"to lead the CIA ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"defended the administration ' s drone execution program before Congress on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that in war the commander in chief has the right","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"to order a targeted killing","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"- but agreeing","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"that Congress should be more involved","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"in knowing what is happening .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Mr. Brennan ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"who is Mr. Obama ' s homeland security adviser","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and is considered one of the key architects of the war on terrorism in recent years ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"also said","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"he is not sure","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"whether interrogation techniques such as waterboarding produced any valuable information from suspected terrorist detainees .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"In a hearing","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"interrupted repeatedly by anti-war protesters ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Brennan denied","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"he had leaked classified information to reporters","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and told the Senate Select Committee on Intelligence","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that he will try to work with Capitol Hill","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"so that lawmakers are aware of the administration ' s operations in the war on terrorism .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Senators homed in on targeted killings by armed unmanned aerial vehicles ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"begun under President George W. Bush","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"and dramatically expanded by Mr. Obama .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"The drone program has come under scrutiny","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"after the Obama administration used it","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to kill an American citizen","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"living in Yemen .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"\" I understand","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"you can ' t have co-commanders in chief ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"but having the executive","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"being the prosecutor , the judge , the jury and the executioner all in one is very contrary to the traditions and the laws of this country , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"said Sen. Angus S. King Jr. , Maine independent .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Brennan replied","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that this was not a judicial proceeding .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" The actions","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"that we take on the counterterrorism front , again ,","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"are to take actions against individuals","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"where we believe","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that the intelligence base is so strong","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"and the nature of the threat is so grave and serious , as well as imminent ,","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"that we have no recourse","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"except to take this action","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"that may involve a lethal strike , \"","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"With some senators threatening to delay Mr. Brennan ' s nomination","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"to be CIA director","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"until more information is disclosed ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"the White House late Wednesday said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"it would provide to the committee legal memos","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"detailing advice about the drone program .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"NBC News this week obtained and released a 16-page Justice Department memo","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"laying out the legal justification for the program .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Three Americans are known to have been killed by the program - all of them in Yemen and all by missile strikes from drones .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"The three are radical Islamic preacher Anwar al-Awlaki , a senior leader in al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"( AQAP ) ;","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"his 16-year-old son , Abdulrahman al-Awlaki ; and AQAP propagandist Samir Khan .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"U.S. officials have said","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that al-Awlaki was targeted directly","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"only because he had an \" operational role \"","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"in recruiting and training suicide terrorists","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"including the Nigerian would-be \" underwear bomber \" Umar Farouk Abdulmutallab .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"The other two were killed in strikes","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"targeting other AQAP leaders .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Several Republicans closely questioned Mr. Brennan about leaks to the news media","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"regarding Obama administration national security successes .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Brennan denied","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that he was the source of any of them .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"\" I never provided classified information to reporters , \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Mr. Brennan said .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that his contacts with the news media were arranged by the White House press office","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and aimed at explaining administration policy .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Sen. Ron Wyden , Oregon Democrat , told the hearing","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that Congress , and eventually the American public , needed to see the documents","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"outlining the legal basis for the targeted-killing program .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"\" We ' ve got to see any and all opinions before the vote \" on the nomination ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Mr. Wyden said .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"He also called for the legal opinions to be made public","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"so that Americans could judge for themselves the exact extent of the authority","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"President Obama asserts","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"to kill U.S. citizens","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"without charge or trial","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"if they are senior al Qaeda leaders","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who can not be captured .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"\" What it really goes to is the issue of checks and balances , \"","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Mr. King asked Mr. Brennan to allow the judicial branch to oversee targeted killings of U.S. citizens ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"as it authorized intelligence surveillance against Americans , through the Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"( FISA )","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"court - a secret tribunal","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"that grants warrants for the electronic and physical surveillance of Americans","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"suspected of espionage or terrorism .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"\" I would like to suggest to you","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"that you consider a FISA court-type process ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"where an American citizen is going to be targeted for a lethal strike , \"","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"Mr. King told Mr. Brennan .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"\" At least that would be some check , \"","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Mr. King said .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"\" I have great confidence in you .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"I have great confidence in President Obama .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"But all the lessons of history are ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"it shouldn ' t matter who ' s in charge ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"because we should have procedures and processes in place","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that will protect us . \"","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Some Republicans asked Mr. Brennan","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"whether the administration ' s expanded use of the lethal strikes by remotely piloted drone aircraft grew from its decision","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"to abjure the capture , detention and harsh interrogation techniques","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"employed by the Bush administration .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"\" Is your testimony today","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"that the huge increase in the number of lethal strikes has no connection to the change in the Obama administration ' s detention policy ? \"","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"said Sen. Susan M. Collins , Maine Republican .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"\" Because obviously ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"if we ' re capturing a terrorist ,","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"we have the opportunity","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"to interrogate that individual","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"and perhaps learn of ongoing plots .","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"if the strike is done ,","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"that opportunity is lost . \"","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"\" There ' s never been occasion","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"that I ' m aware of","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"where we had the opportunity","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"to capture a terrorist","depth":15},{"id":125,"text":"and we didn ' t","depth":15},{"id":126,"text":"and we decided to take a lethal strike , \"","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"replied Mr. Brennan .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"\" So certainly there is no correlation there . \"","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"He added","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"that the expanding use of drones was in part a result of \" the maturation of capabilities and insights into [ al Qaeda ]","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"plots","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"as a result of the investment","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"that was made in the previous administration . \"","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Other Republicans focused on questioning Mr. Brennan about administration leaks to the media .","depth":3},{"id":135,"text":"\" I engaged in discussions with reporters about classified issues","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"that they might have had access to","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"because of unfortunate leaks of classified information ,","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"and I frequently work with reporters , if not editors of newspapers ,","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"to keep out of the public domain some of this country ' s most important secrets , \"","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Mr. Brennan said .","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"\" Whenever I deal with reporters ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"I do so at the request of the White House press office","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"and they set the ground rules , \"","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":145,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"that he voluntary cooperated with the Department of Justice investigation into the leak of information about a double agent inside al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"( AQAP )","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"who helped U.S. and allied agencies foil an underwear bomb plot .","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Mr. Brennan said","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"he had \" been interviewed on it \"","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"and his office turned over \" all relevant materials , \"","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"including any notes of the conference call .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"He denied","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"that a statement","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"he made in a conference call with former officials last year about the plot","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"had compromised intelligence sources and methods .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"The call had been arranged","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"because the former officials were all going on news programs","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"to discuss the foiling of the plot ,","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"which targeted U.S. aviation .","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"Mr. Brennan said , in a statement","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"later repeated publicly by several of the former officials ,","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"that the United States had \" inside control \" of the plot","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"and that the underwear bomb was never a threat to American aviation .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"Later that day , news agencies broke the story","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"that an a U.S. allied agency had an agent inside the AQAP cell","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"planning the bombing .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"Mr. Brennan said","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"he needed to explain","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"that the U.S. had \" inside control , \"","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"because during the time of the plot","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"- around the first anniversary of the Navy SEAL raid on Osama bin Laden ' s compound in Pakistan -","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"he and other officials had reassured","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"that there was no specific actionable intelligence about threats or plots .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"\" We had said publicly","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"that there was no active plot at the time of the bin Laden anniversary , \"","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"Mr. Brennan is a 25-year career intelligence officer","depth":3},{"id":179,"text":"who served in the Bush administration as the first head of the National Counterterrorism Center .","depth":3},{"id":180,"text":"In 2008 , he was a close adviser to Mr. Obama in the Senate .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":361,"left":358,"right":360,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":358,"left":314,"right":357,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":314,"left":226,"right":313,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":202,"right":225,"relatio